import React, { useEffect, useRef } from 'react' import './linechart.scss' export default function LineChart1 () { const divRef = useRef(null) useEffect(() => { var myChart = echarts.init(divRef.current) var option = { title: { text: '关键产品收率计划与实际对比' }, visualMap: [ { show: false, type: 'continuous', seriesIndex: 0, min: 0, max: 600 } ], tooltip: { trigger: 'axis' }, legend: { data: ['计划收率', '实际收率'] }, grid: { left: '3%', right: '4%', bottom: '3%', containLabel: true }, xAxis: { type: 'category', boundaryGap: false, data: [ '2020-6', '2020-7', '2020-8', '2020-9', '2020-10', '2020-11', '2020-12', '2021-1', '2021-2', '2021-3', '2021-4', '2021-5', '2021-6', '2021-7', '2021-8', '2021-9', '2021-10', '2021-11', '2021-12', '2022-1', '2022-2' ] }, yAxis: { type: 'value' }, series: [ { name: '计划收率', showSymbol: false, type: 'line', data: [ 170, 182, 148, 160, 290, 200, 310, 340, 305, 190, 270, 150, 138, 282, 191, 300, 290, 280, 250, 292, 250 ] }, { name: '实际收率', showSymbol: false, type: 'line', data: [ 150, 170, 140, 154, 240, 180, 290, 280, 270, 240, 280, 250, 300, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '' ] } ] } myChart.setOption(option) }, []) return (
) }
